wikipedia_page.main: Lawrence Harvey (born 29 January 1973) is an English-born former international footballer for the Turks and Caicos Islands national football team.Harvey was eligible to play for Turks and Caicos Islands as FIFA eligibility rules permit British passport holders to represent British Overseas Territories at international football in FIFA-recognised matches following two years residency. He fulfills the criteria having once worked in TCI as a quantity surveyor.

response: *Lawrence Harvey (born 1972), formerly of the Turks and Caicos Islands national football team, has worked in Burwell as a quantity surveyor.
